meanings: (사람을) meet, see; (처음으로) (formal) encounter; (우연히) come across, run[bump] into
초대와 방문 I was with somebody.
초대와 방문 Sorry, I had to meet someone.
이성교제 I wanna see you more often after this.

meanings: 약속 I'd really like to see you this Sunday.
